dct_title_s: Relative Positions of Present and Former Pierhead and Bulkhead lines on East Side of Delaware River between Erie Street and Federal Street
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Federal Street to Erie Street in the city of Camden along the Delaware River. Map shows the proposed bulkhead and pierhead lines, as well as some property grants to John F. Starr, Alexander Cooper, and Samuel B. Garrison.
